  "parent": "ccs",
  "notes": "Georgian (Kartuli), official language of Georgia. Written in Mkhedruli script. Three-way consonant distinction: voiced (ბ,გ,დ,ვ,ზ,ჟ,ჯ,ძ), aspirated (თ,ფ,ქ,ჩ,ც,ხ,ჰ), ejective (კ,პ,ტ,ყ,წ,ჭ). Complex consonant clusters. Kartvelian language family unrelated to Indo-European.",
